cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with face template protection, which is a subfield of computer vision and biometrics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses error correction using a neural network, which falls under the category of machine learning and deep learning, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories as well. The paper also uses multiple face databases, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
